                  </persName>
            . I am a butcher; I am a leading man at the victualling-office. The prisoner worked there for me two winters, and behaved extreamly well.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17720109-50-person549">
                  John
                   Geary
               <interp inst="t17720109-50-person549" type="surname" value="Geary"></interp>
