                     <interp inst="t17720109-50-person549" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I work in the victualling-office. I have known the prisoner two years; he was always esteemed an honest man; I never heard any thing amiss of his character.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17720109-50-person550">
